snippet.title: Redeemer Enhanced Edition | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Redeemer: Enhanced Edition is an intense Brawler where you will punch, hack and blast your way through enemies using fists, hammers, fire arms and even the environment. This is the brawler for those who love brawlers and have been waiting for a modern take on the genre.
